RUAppUTFPR-Ap

=============

Para compilar:

1- cd .\beeware-tutorial\
2- cd .\ruapputfprap\
3- Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope Process
3- .\beeware-venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
4- briefcase dev
